                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <locus from="58ra"/>
                            <title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT6171HolyCross">The
                                invention of the Holy Cross by the empress Helena (<date
                                    ref="ethiocal:Hedar8">8th of Ḫǝdār</date>)</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ነገረ፡ አስተርእዮተ፡</hi> መስቀሉ፡ ዐቢይ፡
                                    ማሕየ<hi rend="rubric">ዊ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወአምላ</hi>ክነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ <hi
                                    rend="rubric">አመ፡ ፰ ለኅዳር፡ በመዋዕ</hi>ለ፡ ቈስጠንጢኖስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ <hi
                                    rend="rubric">ዐቢይ፡ መሀይምን፡ ኄር፡</hi></incipit>

                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                            <locus from="67ra"/>
                            <title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT1651Homily">Homily of
