                                four beasts (<date ref="ethiocal:Hedar8">8th of
                                Ḫǝdār</date>)</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ድርሳን፡ ዘብፁዕ፡ ወቅ</hi>ዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡
                                ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ <hi rend="rubric">ዘቈስጠንጢንያ፡ በእንተ፡ ፬፡ </hi>እንስሳ፡ ዐቢያት፡
                                    መን<hi rend="rubric">ፈሳዊያን፡ አመ፡ ፰ ለኅዳር፡ </hi>ዘይትነበብ፡ በሰላመ፡
                                እግዚአብሔር፡ አሜን።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                            <locus from="77r"/>
                            <title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="LIT6174Severus318">Treatise of
                                    <persName ref="PRS8788Severos">Severus (of Ašmunayn)</persName>
                                on the Council of the 318 Fathers (at Nicaea)</title>
                            <note>In the upper margin, there is a reading note that names this text
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዝክረ፡ ማኅበር፡</foreign> and suggests to
                                read it on <date ref="ethiocal:ethiocal:Hedar9">9th of Ḫǝdār</date>.
                               </note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ነገር፡ በእንተ፡ ማኅበር፡ ሠለስቱ፡ ምእት፡ ዐሠርቱ፡ ወሰመንቱ፡ ዘአባ፡
                                ሳዊሮስ፡ አመ፡ ፱፡ ለኅዳር፡ በጽሐ፡ መልእክትከ፡ እኁየ፡ መሀይምን፡ ወብፁዕ፡ ይዕቀብከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡
                                ለቅኔሁ፡ ወይርድእከ፡ ለሥምረቱ፡ ወይመግብከ፡ በዓቂቦቱ፡ ተዝካር፡ አንብቦትከ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዘጽሐፎ፡ ስዒድ፡
                                ወልደ፡ ጰጥሪቅ፡ ወሰመዮ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሓሳብ፡ ወትካዙ፡ ዘውስተ፡ ልብከ፡ በእንተ፡ ዘነበበ፡ ዕረፍተ፡ ለሕግነ፡
                                ከመ፡ ዘይጌጊዩ፡ ወዘከመ፡ ይዌልጡ፡ ሃይማኖተ፡ ርትዕት። ወይወጥኑ፡ ካልአ፡ ሀይማኖተ። ወሰአልከኒ፡
                                ይዕቀብከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በጸጋሁ፡ ሰአልከኒ፡ እግበር፡ መጽሓፈ፡ ዕቁም፡ ሓሳበ፡ ፍካሬ፡ ሀይማኖት፡ እንተ፡
                                ዜነዉ፡ አበው፡ ሐዋርያት፡ እስመ፡ እሙንቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ሕግ፡ ወተፈነዉ፡ እም፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በርትዕት፡
                                ሃይማኖት:</incipit>
                            <note> While cataloguing this manuscript, <persName ref="PRS1071dAbbadi"/>
                                notes the following: <cit>
                                    <quote>This meeting took place on the 9th of Hidar.(</quote>
                                </cit><cit>
                                    <quote xml:lang="fr">Cette réunion eut lieu le 9 hidar.</quote>
                                </cit>) Cataloguing this manuscript, <persName ref="PRS3182ContiRo"/>
                                notes the following: <cit>
                                    <quote>see the <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFabb155">n.128</ref>,
                                        III. The work is also known as <foreign xml:lang="gez"
                                            >Maṣḥafa ḫedār</foreign>, "Book of ḫedār", its reading
                                        is prescribed for the 7th day of the month of ḫedār.</quote>
                                </cit> (<cit>
                                    <quote xml:lang="fr">voir le <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFabb155"
                                            >n.128</ref>, III. L'ouvrage est connu aussi sous le nom
                                        de <foreign xml:lang="gez">Maṣḥafa ḫedār</foreign> "Livre de
                                        ḫedār", la lecture en est ordonnée pour le 7 du mois de
                                        ḫedār.</quote>
                                </cit>). <persName ref="PRS3082Chaine"/>, while recataloguing this
                                manuscript, suggests that this text starts on f.71, but this must be
                                a typo.</note>

